  "detailed_description": "&quot;Otawamure&quot; is a Japanese word meaning  &quot;to play around, to fool around or toy with&quot;. This VR experience provides a virtual space where you can feel \u201cotawamure\u201d yourself while playing with tender objects. The space has three activities inside. In one of them, you\u2019ll find yourself carefully cutting eggs using a string, trying to slice them just right. Another will give you a hand fan to blow a set of quirky objects away. And in the last one jiggly, bouncy puddings will drop from the sky for you to catch. None of these experiences has a specific goal or objective, but we hope they can help you experience \u201cotawamure\u201d.",
